{"tid":635271,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"終於知石原里美似邊個","createTime":"2018-04-20T04:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T15:03:56.000Z","uid":82917,"like":9,"dislike":164,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f12b3f6be0069f6e44495bc047080b40af12ef","tid":635271,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/115859_4106cef8fc121b7e670eece684a5dbec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F115859_4106cef8fc121b7e670eece684a5dbec.png&h=8a5b176f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/115902_23b72aa4cc486987e740c7338b838a00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F115902_23b72aa4cc486987e740c7338b838a00.png&h=d4fce0df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/115919_e4e4f1a452c3be1e5434d02a801cd709.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F115919_e4e4f1a452c3be1e5434d02a801cd709.png&h=641fe0f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/115923_00e586efc43b6d9010afbbd52d438bfc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F115923_00e586efc43b6d9010afbbd52d438bfc.png&h=64d88fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/115926_a25616241ba1558ff6c3bade86da4655.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F115926_a25616241ba1558ff6c3bade86da4655.png&h=6a92de7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/115927_c3ee1bed93031ae415dd306d2f04543c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F115927_c3ee1bed93031ae415dd306d2f04543c.png&h=8f63742c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/115931_d04c3fe004580a87300cb8c95e9936c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F115931_d04c3fe004580a87300cb8c95e9936c0.png&h=1b82e764&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/115939_8b1a5fa3203b809a32a27ab999794c9c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F115939_8b1a5fa3203b809a32a27ab999794c9c.png&h=f3df1b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直都覺得佢好似許瑋倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n許瑋倫（1978年11月13日－2007年1月28日），台灣女演員，畢業於華岡藝術學校、淡江大學法國語文學系。代表作有偶像劇《十八歲的約定》。2007年1月26日，因車禍重傷，兩日後傷重不治，於台中市澄清醫院中港院區去世，得年28歲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再搵返石原啲相，某啲角度真係幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/120132_11805f67df060366fdee02a21f53ca42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F120132_11805f67df060366fdee02a21f53ca42.png&h=f6e12cc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/120138_e8e6505ec8eec28f1e834b94b55e7515.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F120138_e8e6505ec8eec28f1e834b94b55e7515.png&h=26a8804b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/120146_32c923f088b6e3bdcff60dd6d79bb4fe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F120146_32c923f088b6e3bdcff60dd6d79bb4fe.png&h=85778415&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/120154_6691e4d862f8e6134e15dece8a6f5528.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F120154_6691e4d862f8e6134e15dece8a6f5528.png&h=bc1ebdad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/120204_089e0b452325e83b1756ae589ea8e644.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F120204_089e0b452325e83b1756ae589ea8e644.png&h=2ff0ab35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我知呢幾張冇咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係拎黎做對比，一陣再擺石原J圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知連登仲有冇人識許瑋倫呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea598fddfa7987da9b242203ba7afc58d73069f9","tid":635271,"uid":167721,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:04:31.000Z","msg":"想同佢哋3p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cfcf237863dc1263bda50825a4f36ab86377cd","tid":635271,"uid":82917,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"ea598fddfa7987da9b242203ba7afc58d73069f9","tid":635271,"uid":167721,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:04:31.000Z","msg":"想同佢哋3p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。。。<br />\n人地都去左咁多年。。。"},{"pid":"d29eb55b950e410dc74161834e357e919d6570c1","tid":635271,"uid":116530,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:06:38.000Z","msg":"石原吊打佢"},{"pid":"648ae179d56eaf5b